- [GROANS]

1247
01:16:27,680 --> 01:16:29,637
We gotta jam! Motherfucker's up there!

1248
01:16:29,720 --> 01:16:30,710
- [GUNSHOTS CONTINUE]
- [GRUNTS]

1249
01:16:33,080 --> 01:16:34,514
Where is he?

1250
01:16:34,880 --> 01:16:35,996
You're hit.

1251
01:16:36,080 --> 01:16:37,434
- Did you see him?
- No.

1252
01:16:37,520 --> 01:16:39,000
Okay. Fuck.

1253
01:16:43,200 --> 01:16:44,953
Okay, I saw him that time!

1254
01:16:45,040 --> 01:16:46,235
Okay, I got an idea.

1255
01:16:46,320 --> 01:16:48,357
I'll lay down some cover fire,
you run to the other car.

1256
01:16:48,440 --> 01:16:49,635
He won't be able to track you there, okay?

1257
01:16:49,720 --> 01:16:50,710
What?

1258
01:16:50,800 --> 01:16:52,280
He'll be takin' shots at me,
he won't even see you. Get going!

1259
01:16:52,360 --> 01:16:55,000
- Dad, you're hurt!
- Get in the other car and fuck off!

1260
01:16:55,080 --> 01:16:58,234
No, no. If you think that I'm leaving you,
then you're out of your fucking mind!

1261
01:16:58,320 --> 01:16:59,834
- Do not run until I start firing!
- No!

1262
01:16:59,920 --> 01:17:01,320
- I'm gonna count to three. One!
- No!

1263
01:17:01,400 --> 01:17:02,754
- Two...
- No!

1264
01:17:02,840 --> 01:17:04,160
Count to a million if you want to!

1265
01:17:04,240 --> 01:17:06,152
If you think that
I'm leaving here without you,

1266
01:17:06,240 --> 01:17:08,311
then you don't know me!

1267
01:17:08,400 --> 01:17:11,234
All this time, and you never
even fucking knew me!

1268
01:17:12,560 --> 01:17:14,711
What? Okay. Okay.

1269
01:17:16,640 --> 01:17:18,836
- It's nice to meet you.
- [GUNSHOTS FIRING]

1270
01:17:19,400 --> 01:17:22,040
Okay, I got another idea.
Let's go together.

1271
01:17:22,120 --> 01:17:23,634
- On your count or mine?
- Yours.

1272
01:17:23,720 --> 01:17:24,790
- Okay, let's go!
- Okay.

1273
01:17:24,880 --> 01:17:26,109
[GROANS] God... Go, go, go!

1274
01:17:32,680 --> 01:17:33,750
[YELLS]

1275
01:17:34,040 --> 01:17:35,030
[GROANS]

1276
01:17:40,280 --> 01:17:41,316
[ENGINE STARTS]

1277
01:17:48,960 --> 01:17:51,794
- Dad!
- Hey. You okay?

1278
01:17:51,880 --> 01:17:53,792
- I'm okay.
- Good.

1279
01:17:55,120 --> 01:17:57,077
Oh, no! Oh, fuck!

1280
01:17:58,480 --> 01:18:00,039
Dad, he's coming.

1281
01:18:05,600 --> 01:18:06,670
I don't know where he is.

1282
01:18:06,760 --> 01:18:09,195
Yeah, he's coming. Come here. Come here.

1283
01:18:09,800 --> 01:18:11,234
Be still.

1284
01:18:11,320 --> 01:18:13,835
- Be very, very still.
- I'm so sorry.

1285
01:18:50,480 --> 01:18:51,914
[BOTH GROANING]

1286
01:18:54,840 --> 01:18:57,594
I got him! I got him! I got you!

1287
01:18:57,680 --> 01:18:59,194
[LAUGHING]

1288
01:19:02,040 --> 01:19:03,076
Oh, shit!

1289
01:19:04,280 --> 01:19:06,511
This is not good. Oh, fuck!

1290
01:19:06,600 --> 01:19:08,114
Dead motherfucker!

1291
01:19:10,000 --> 01:19:11,320
The other one. Get your head down.

1292
01:19:11,400 --> 01:19:12,720
- There's the other one, the boyfriend.
- Stop, stop!

1293
01:19:12,800 --> 01:19:14,712
- He's out there.
- Dad, he's gone. He's gone!

1294
01:19:14,800 --> 01:19:16,200
- Where did he...
- He's gone, okay?

1295
01:19:16,280 --> 01:19:17,396
I gotta go get us help.

1296
01:19:17,520 --> 01:19:20,433
No, you stay here.
Don't leave me, stay here, please.

1297
01:19:20,520 --> 01:19:21,670
Yeah.

1298
01:19:22,400 --> 01:19:24,073
Yeah, yeah.

1299
01:19:24,160 --> 01:19:25,992
Just let me look at you.

1300
01:19:32,480 --> 01:19:34,392
Your hair came out good.

1301
01:19:36,480 --> 01:19:40,554
Look, kid, I'm really bad.
Here, take this gun.

1302
01:19:41,480 --> 01:19:43,199
I got nothing better to give ya.

1303
01:19:43,280 --> 01:19:45,636
I never gave you anything
and now I got nothing to give you.

1304
01:19:45,720 --> 01:19:47,871
Dad, Dad! That is not true.

1305
01:19:47,960 --> 01:19:48,996
I lost ya...

1306
01:19:49,080 --> 01:19:51,072
Dad! Look at me! Look at me!

1307
01:19:52,280 --> 01:19:53,999
You did not lose me.

1308
01:19:54,080 --> 01:19:58,040
I am not lost,
I am right here with you, okay? Okay?

1309
01:19:58,800 --> 01:20:00,632
I'm not gonna leave.

1310
01:20:01,240 --> 01:20:02,515
- Okay?
- Okay.

1311
01:20:02,600 --> 01:20:04,034
Look at me.

1312
01:20:04,120 --> 01:20:06,555
- It's just you and me.
- Okay.

1313
01:20:06,760 --> 01:20:09,753
I'm not gonna leave, ever. I promise.

1314
01:20:12,480 --> 01:20:13,880
You sure are a good girl.

1315
01:20:14,960 --> 01:20:17,555
You sure are. You sure are.

1316
01:20:21,040 --> 01:20:22,235
Dad?

1317
01:20:26,280 --> 01:20:27,316
[CRYING]

1318
01:20:38,160 --> 01:20:39,833
[SIREN WAILING IN THE DISTANCE]

1319
01:20:54,520 --> 01:20:57,194
On your knees! Hands behind your head!

1320
01:20:57,640 --> 01:20:58,630
[DOOR BUZZING]

1321
01:21:02,320 --> 01:21:04,357
[LYDIA] A year ago, I stopped running.

1322
01:21:06,120 --> 01:21:10,353
I stopped listening
to all of my worst instincts

1323
01:21:10,440 --> 01:21:12,909
and all the worst people.

1324
01:21:26,160 --> 01:21:28,038
I'll just tell you this.

1325
01:21:29,080 --> 01:21:30,912
I've been sober a year.

1326
01:21:33,640 --> 01:21:38,999
I miss my father so much,
that I can't sleep some nights, but...

1327
01:21:40,320 --> 01:21:42,994
...I tell myself that
he's watching over me.

1328
01:21:45,920 --> 01:21:50,517
Sometimes, there's this shame

1329
01:21:51,040 --> 01:21:53,509
that almost breaks my back, but...

1330
01:21:54,840 --> 01:21:56,957
I tell myself,

1331
01:21:57,320 --> 01:22:00,552
"When you owe your life to someone,

1332
01:22:02,160 --> 01:22:03,958
you better live it."

1333
01:22:05,120 --> 01:22:08,591
So, I just say...

1334
01:22:11,600 --> 01:22:13,000
"Thank you."

